sequenceDiagram
    participant Cliente
    participant FastAPI
    participant PDFExtractor
    participant OllamaExtractor
    participant Calculator
    participant Repository

    Cliente->>FastAPI: POST /calculate-from-pdf (PDF + total)
    FastAPI->>PDFExtractor: extract_text(file)
    PDFExtractor-->>FastAPI: contract_text
    FastAPI->>OllamaExtractor: extract_rules(text)
    OllamaExtractor-->>FastAPI: ContractRules (actor, rule, value)
    FastAPI->>Calculator: calculate(request)
    Calculator->>Repository: save(response)
    Calculator-->>FastAPI: PayrollResponse
    FastAPI-->>Cliente: JSON con liquidación